Web of Seduction;;1999;;Unrated;;Drama,Mystery,Thriller;;5.4;;Blain Brown;;Lauren Hays,Eric Acsell,Tracy Ryan,Stephan Camus,Michael George,Nancy O'Brien;;In this erotic tale of suspense, seduction, and murder, a cleaning woman finds herself working for two wives who are wealthy, idle, and ignored by their husbands. The maid persuades the two woman to kill each other's spouses and live happily ever after off the proceeds of their hubbies' valuable art collections. However, the plan does not go as expected, and the conspirators find that their own lives are in danger.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0214299/